touch: (Psst, Master, there anything you wanna do? And I mean anything. Accompanying her master is a maid's duty, after all!)
touch2: I mean... This is pretty sudden... But that's not to say I hate it!
win_mvp: Woohoo! Master! Oh, we can't take a selfie while I'm hugging you? Ahahah, right... One sec. There. We good now?

detail: Owner! Squeeeeze! Are you free right meow? I could make some yummy sweets for you!
home: Owner! Mew came back early just to see me! It's good I left the office early to see mew too!
login: Owneeeeer! Mrreow~ Mmhh~ Owner? Wakey wakey, Owner! Your favourite kitten is here!
main_extra: Now time for the whipped cream... Oh nooo! Help, Owner! I spilled cream on the floor!|When you get busy with work, I do as well! ...Wait, how does that work?|I've got a pack of orange juice for you, Owner! Give it a taste – it's great! I got it from the vending machine outside Akashi's store!
touch: Owner...?
touch2: Huh? What is it, Owner?

feeling5: The truth can occasionally be cruel, so exposing others to it won't necessarily lead to happiness. Sometimes, spending life behind a mask is the easier way. But with you, Commander... I can sincerely feel comfortable showing you my true self.
headtouch: Do you think this child's play is enough to satisfy me?
home: Welcome back, and well done on your mission. Here are some fresh donuts and black tea. Please enjoy a well-earned break.
login: Commander, welcome back. You know... I think Master would be a more affectionate term of address. What do you think?
main_extra: I maintain a facade of elegance and politeness in reliable maid mode, but you don't seem especially interested in that. This is a problem... How should I interact with you?|Favours must be repaid in kind with donuts. That is the first law of nature.|Work mode disengaged. "Now I'm in 'Commander, spoil me' mode! M-Master~ I made donuts for you. Wanna try them... hehe, in my room later?"
mission: If you're tired, I'm sure nobody will mind if you take a break before you handle your missions.
mission_complete: Your rewards are right this way. "Aww, no donuts? So sad~... You'll really buy me some? Hooray♡"
touch: Are you interested in what's inside my skirt?
touch2: "Geez~ I didn't know you had such special interests."

detail: Commander, today's reading is not on the Royal Knights? Aww... Well, if you recommend it, I'll gladly read it!
home: Leave the preparations to Belfast, and the combat reports to me! Such are the duties of the maid and the knight, yes!
login: Commander, Renown has free time today and is standing by! Please give me your orders! ...Something other than "go play," please!
main: I'm not... sleepy... at all... Commander, I'll... protect you... Zzz... My eyes...|I'm really cute? ...Um, Commander, I'm glad to receive your praise, but I'd rather be complimented on my abilities rather than my looks!|nil
touch: Renown has no need for a sugar rush at this time... B-but, maybe just one piece of candy...!

battle: For the glory of Her Majesty and the Commander!
detail: Should I prepare a snack for you? I'm not skilled enough to be able to boast to others like George does, but my cooking won't disappoint, either.
expedition: Commissions have been completed. Let's go greet the girls together.
feeling5: Love based on pretense is a vile thing. I give myself to you as I am, and I accept you for who you are. No matter how many mistakes you make, I can overlook them all, because my eyes are cloudy with tears of happiness. That's what lovers do, after all.
home: A toast to our victory. Never forget that you are the reason that everyone can enjoy this peace for yet another day.
login: Managing the fleet is complicated and difficult. If there's anything I can help out with, let me know.
lose: A light heart lives long. Don't be too hard on yourself.
main: nil|Repulse, Vampire, and Hood, and Eugen and Bismarck... It seems there'll be no risk of boredom while I'm by your side.|I'm used to taking care of Her Highness' needs, so it's perfectly fine for you to make absurd requests from time to time. On top of that, I'll flawlessly complete your request and make you fall in love with me all over again... Hehe, how does that sound?
touch: Is it already time for the tea party?
touch2: You know exactly what this means, right? Hehe.

battle: May these eyes sink into deep crimson...
feeling5: O sinful serpent, thou hast chosen to entwine thyself around me. Dedicate thy love to me for all of eternity— and in return, accept my love, and the right to embrace me.
login: O, Commander who hath earned my adoration, what is thy desire?
main: Thy existence has greatly influenced my fighting style — Yes, it resonates with thy passionate eyes, and my pupils also become stained with thy blood-red colour. |I shalt not giveth thee to Wales, George, Anson, or Howe. Thou art my trophy, and the proof of my conquest.|Pitiable Scharnhorst, who knows not the value of thy skin, thy eyes, thy very body... Yes, Commander, thou art the world to me.
touch2: Melt into one, be it thou or myself, be it anything in existence—
win_mvp: Melt before the crimson apocalypse. Merely tearing thy husks apart is no longer enough to sate me.

feeling5: Hehehe, let's plan for our next date, love. Speaking of which, I've heard of a place with famously delicious cookies. How does that sound?
home: Splendid work, love. Have a cookie and get some rest, then we'll start on the after-battle report.
login: Welcome back. Can I keep you company until the night arrives, love?
main: My sisters can be rather headstrong at times. If they give you any trouble, you can turn to me, love.|nil|It seems my cookies were adored, but my performance failed to garner any reactions...
touch: You'd like a massage? It would be my pleasure.
touch2: I can see why you'd do that. Hehehe~

feeling5: I don't care if I win or lose... A-after all, what's more important is that I get to be with you, right...? You agree?! ...W-well then, let's have a rematch!
home: My assistant, how fares the war situation? N-nothing out of the ordinary, hopefully?
login: You're here! Good timing, let's go over today's itinerary!
main: Hey, what's taking so long? ...The black tea still isn't ready? I'm already used to the flavor of your tea, so don't keep me waiting too long...|Charisma might be important, but what people truly flock to is your talent and sincerity.|nil
touch: Huh? What is it? Are you even listening to me?

battle: I bear no grudges against you, but... Let the battle begin!
feeling5: Your Excellency, I do not consider you to be weak—and as such, I don't protect you as a member of the Royal Knights, but as a woman who loves you. That is my simple wish, that which makes me happiest... O-of course, I plan on protecting you as a subordinate as well...
home: I'm so relieved that you're alright... Thank goodness... I really wanted to be out there to make sure you were safe, you know? Ehe♪
login: Welcome back, Your Excellency. Hehehe, after seeing your face, I can't help but feel like today's going to be a great day.
mail: Whew... I brought the mail over, Your Excellency.
main_extra: That battleship from the Northern Parliament... is truly knowledgeable of the etiquettes of the Royal Navy. I am truly impressed.|If you're feeling tired, how about taking a rest for a bit? I shall be protecting Your Excellency by your side, so you need not worry.
touch: So you want to chat? ...I-I apologize! You need something done immediately, don't you?
touch2: At least w-wait until we get somewhere else to do that...
win_mvp: I don't enjoy fighting, but... I'm doing this to protect those I care about!

battle: Yes! YES! It's my time to shine!
detail: See? This is an unassuming flat – unlike Lady Formidable's place. A knight's residence should be orderly and free of– Don't go digging through my shelves!
expedition: The commission team's back. Let's head out to meet them. And while we're at it, let us sortie!
feeling5: *sigh*... I have no idea how you've put up with this job for so long, Commander. Let me tell you a good way to vent some stress. You go out at sea for an exercise, and... A-a date?! Wh-wh-why are you bringing THAT up all of a sudden?!
headtouch: If you want to pat my head... then I guess that's fine.
login: Ah, there you are. Yeah, yeah, I'm here with you. That's my duty as your secretary and guard... But truth be told, I do it just because I want to.
lose: You picked the wrong fight. Try harder next time if you don't want to make fools of yourselves.
main_extra: A sortie is an opportunity for me to flourish! The glory is nice too, but I think we can all agree the best part is showing the world what we're made of!|Being as graceful as Lady Hood would be a huge undertaking... M-mind you, I'm not saying it would be impossible!|Royal breakfast is all right, that much I'll personally vouch for! If you're curious to try it, I'm willing to cook it myself!|If you need some enemies sent to the scrapyard, take me out of the dock and send me on a sortie! Preferably with Lady Victorious – she and I would likely get along!|What? There's a package for me? ...Look, I can explain... It's nothing noteworthy, really... Just, you know, some cute comics.
mission: A new mission's come– Oh god, this one's going to be a pain.
skill: This... This move is too cringeworthy to name, so forget it!
touch: Whatever you need done, give me the honour. A knight is always ready to serve.
touch2: I-I'm not some idiot who'll admit to liking this, no way...
win_mvp: Behold! My royal sabreee! ...Wait, what? They're all gone? Oh god, I can feel everyone's cringing at me!

battle: I'll do my best to keep up with everyone...!
detail: Lord Commander, has a training round ever come your way during an exercise? I see... Knowing that it's happened to you is a bit of a relief... I-I promise I'm not teasing you!
login: It is good to see your safe return, Lord Commander. Erm... You don't have to be so considerate when you're just opening the door.
main_extra: Revenge, w-wait! Geez... She left before I could tell her where those papers were going. What do I do now?|When I'm with you, Lord Commander, I feel like I don't have to worry about stray bullets... Uh, that was just an example! I promise I'm not trying to use you as a human shield!
touch: D-d-do you need something? I'll do everything in my power to tackle whatever problem needs solving!
touch2: If this is something I can do for you, Lord Commander... *blushes*
win_mvp: I-I can fight if I put my mind to it!

battle: I'll prove that I can fight...!
detail: The outfit I wore during our outing is right over here. I went ahead and ironed it, so there's not a single wrinkle on it! Heheh, maybe I'll wear it again... next time we go out?
expedition: The commission team has returned. Our home is by your side, Commander.
home: Welcome back, Commander. You return victorious as promised, I see. Good job! *pat pat* Heehee!
login: Zzzz... Ah! Is it already time for work? Sorry for oversleeping... I was so excited to be your secretary that I stayed up really late...
main_extra: Ugh... I hope these numbers are right. I'd be a failure of a secretary if I had to ask Langley and the others for help...|Hood, you're even prettier than usual today. And you, Commander, look even... No, you ARE cooler than ever!|If you're going out, let me go with you! Why? Well... We can call it a date! Teehee!♪
mission: Oh, was there correspondence regarding a mission? R-right... Got it!
touch: Would you like me to hold your hand and lead the way?
touch2: Yes, good. Please dote on me.
win_mvp: "My hundred eyes have already foreseen your defeat." And so did the Commander!

detail: Okay, fine. I use my mirror for conversation practice... Stop giggling, it's not funny.
expedition: The commission team is back, Commander.
feeling5: I've become able to just, you know, talk. Like a normal person. With you and other people, I mean. I owe you thanks for helping me come this far. I love you, Commander. I really do.
login: There's that saying that goes, "the early bird catches the worm"... Uh, just try not to starve to death, Commander.
main: If you need my help with something, just say it. But first, try to accomplish it on your own. Or don't, that's fine.|Work is like food, they both have an expiry date. So, need any help finishing your food, so to speak?|nil
main_extra: Intrepid, can you see Perseus? No, I mean, the constellation.
touch: So, are you up for a chat?
upgrade: Thanks a bunch... Well, yeah, didn't you want a thank-you?

detail: While Elder Centaur tends to take after our other Elders and follow what they do, I prefer to learn from them instead. Indeed, I prefer using my brain, just as you do.
expedition: Commander, the girls have returned from their commission~ Heehee, that's not the whispers of the wind you're hearing, but rather my breath~ Did you enjoy it?
feeling5: Commander, did you need me? I know you didn't call for me, but I could just feel it. As our hearts are now connected, I heard your desires upon the wind... Oh, m-my apologies for getting worked up on my own... Umm... love you, my dear.
home: Well done, Commander. As for the after-action report... You'd like me to handle it? Naturally, I'd be delighted to!
login: I want to be a more capable secretary like Elder Centaur... Oh, Commander, I'm awaiting your orders.
main_extra: If I could instruct the others in my unique fighting style, we could perhaps implement new tactics in battle. It's certainly not because I want to be called an Elder myself or anything. Heehee.|Elder Enterprise really can do just about anything... Though if there's any area I can exceed her in, it's probably cooking, housework, or making my way through the forests like Centaur... Um, huh...?|Commander, could you tell me what your favourite book is? I was planning on studying your tastes, just as I have been doing with the other Elders here.|Secretary duties aren't so difficult after all now that I've gotten used to things. The bigger issue is how I can take the initiative... I suppose I'll start by taking on some of the Commander's work... Yes, I think that's exactly what I should do.
touch: I shall indulge the inquisitive Commander's curiosity. Please, take my hand and hold it tight.
touch2: Yes, Commander. Our hearts are connected, now and forever.
win_mvp: Phew... It really does take lots of consistent effort to live up to my Elders' expectations. Nevertheless, the unblemished Albion thusly claims this victory!

battle: Eyes open for my – and the Commander's – prowess!
detail: Ah yes, there's the black cat, hell-bent as always on spying on me... Heehee. Don't be alarmed, Commander. You are always welcome to my room.
expedition: The commission team is back in port. I'm going make like a Sakura cat and beckon them to... I've got it wrong?
feeling5: Oh, something on your mind, Commander? Heehee. I don't reckon you need an incantation. You're here for the sole purpose of seeing me, isn't that right? Missing me is still a problem, and I know when you have one of those.
home: Welcome back, our Seagull of Victory. You've fought admirably. Do you want a pat on the head? Or should I recite an incantation that'll take you straight to dreamland?
login: Good morning, my Honourable Knight. May luck be on our side today. Heehee.
main_extra: Hey, Perseus! Are you in the mood for another tea party with Unicorn? Those biscuits we had last time were simply divine!|Office is all tidied up and I've struck upon the solution to our next task. It's time to... Wait! First, I have to brew some tea for you, Commander!|A swim in the river in the woods? Sounds good! I'll pack my tea set, biscuits, and... Hang on. This sounds an awful lot like a picnic to me...
touch: Need something? Heehee, that's my cue. Eyes open, now!
touch2: There, there. You're my sunshine, Commander.
win_mvp: Victory is ours. Hehe, so, do you have any praise for me, my brave lion of a Commander?

feeling5: Weight and appearances don't bother me as much anymore. We, as ships, can't physically change much anyway, and you're happy with me no matter how I look. We are both irreplaceable to one another, after all.
home: My body weight's still the same as it w– Oh, you're back, Commander. Yeah, it's been business as usual in here.
login: Commander, if you're tired, you could've just stayed in bed, or arrived late if you wanted. All you need do is let me know about it.
main: Low-calorie diets are a healthy habit, Commander. You should give one a try sometime.|I don't really mind showing you my physical exam report. Just to you, Commander.|I've gotten better at talking to all the submarines. Knowing you for so long has helped me substantially improve my social skills.
touch: An invitation for lunch, eh? With you watching over me, I think I can do it. Let's go.
touch2: Despite my weight, I have little meat on my– Wh-what are you doing?!
upgrade: That really hit the spot, thank you. No matter how hard the going may get, I will always keep advancing for you.

battle: Fulmar squadron, Swordfish squadron, prepare to launch!
detail: Commander, I'll take care of the destroyers... Err, WE'LL take care of the destroyers! As long as we're around, no one can do them harm!
login: Commander, I am ready to act. I mean ready to fight, of course! Let us show the enemy the might of a Royal Navy aircraft carrier!
main: What am I thinking? Oh, just about you, and the fleet.|You want to call the destroyer girls here to your office, do you...? Commander, this is a task you must entrust to me, Ark Royal!|The outfit Glorious, Acasta, and Ardent recommended... should go like this. One must be more careful next time.|That little submarine is missing again. Heavens, she's always stealing away into other people's rooms to play hide and seek...
touch2: Commander! N-not here...!
win_mvp: It is thanks to the Commander's guidance that I reach my full potential and seize victory!

detail: The posters on the walls are all my favourite rock stars. I don't usually let anyone see them. You're a special exception, Commander~
expedition: Ding dong ding dong ♪, incoming message from Formidable: Commission complete. Repeat. Commission complete.
home: Commander, I'm going to catch a few winks on the sofa here. Wake me up if anyone comes calling.
login: You're late, Commander. I've been waiting for ages!
mail: Commander, the mail is here. Would you mind getting it yourself?
main: That Ajax, she saw straight through me right away... And yet, I think we get along rather well. I've learned a lot from her.|Haah... I'm back. Those tea parties have some delicious snacks, sure, but they're so dreadfully uptight about bearing and deportment.... Hehehe, Commander, would you mind helping me with my shoes?|Commander, which of my sisters is more your type? The sweet and gentle Illustrious, or the passionate Victorious?
mission: Big Brother, I finished organizing your mission list ♪ ... Hehe, is that your type, Commander?
mission_complete: Commander, do you want your mission rewards or do you want me? You have to choose! ... Hehe, just kidding~
touch: Commander, don't you think Veneto looks a bit dim, cool as she might be?
touch2: Commander, should I be angry? Positively inconsolable?

detail: Would you please describe how gorgeous my dress is? Yes, and kindly don't stop until I feel I've heard enough ♪
home: Commander, are you still busy? I'm afraid I can't be of much assistance, but I can give you a wink to keep your spirits up. Best of luck ♪
login: Hehe~ I've waited for you all this time, Commander. I would've preferred it if you'd come a little sooner, though. Hehehe~
main: Has my hair gotten entangled? How?! I'm always going to such lengths to prevent it! What if Sirius is trying to– Oh, it's all right now? Th-thank you.|Come here for a moment, Commander! Let's straighten out your uniform... There! Perfect!|Commander, I'm sure my sisters all have splendrous dresses, but do not forget about your dear Formidable.
touch: You'd like a dance? Certainly. Allow me to be your first, and hopefully, your favourite partner.
touch2: Commander! I urge you to pat my head at once! Or else I will ignore you for the rest of the party!

detail: Alone in the classroom with a student... What happens next? Heehee, don't worry, I already know. Your eyes have been glued to me for so long already!
home: W-welcome back! I made a boxed lunch for you, Commander. Would you like it now?
main: nil|nil|Time spent with you is so peaceful and nice... Heehee, and I don't have to carry myself with the bearing of a royal lady, either. "I love you, Commander♪"
touch2: Eep?! Commander, you'd better have a good explanation this time! ..."Sorry, honey sweetest"? Now you're just messing with me... Oh, forget it.

battle: On the Commander's name, I shall smite all who stand in our way.
detail: If you're bored, we can go look if the canteen's offering anything new. Let's also pop down to the shop and see what's on sale. Heehee. If you want to kill time, might as well do it with me, right?
feeling5: It's wrong to pray only for you and nobody else. However, you're the very person who pushed me in this direction. It is your mistake – do you know what you must do to rectify it? Yes, you do. You have to throw reason to the wayside and let your throbbing... heart take over. Heehee~♥
headtouch: My prayers are with you, Commander. Now... and forever.
home: Say... Isn't there even a chance you'll drink my tea? You could at least pretend to sip it to let me feel good about myself.
login: While there are many who'll give their all for you, I'm the only one who can answer your prayers at the moment. Heehee♥
main_extra: You're grimacing again... Fine. Come here and lie down. I'll help you let out all those woes and pent-up stress.|Idols, hmm? I suppose Illustrious and the rest have what it takes. I'd also say that you're like the entire fleet's idol, Commander. Heehee♥|I don't mind if you're biased or pick favourites, just don't look away when we're all to ourselves. If you do... Well, I'll put a curse on you. Heehee♥|Virtuous people losing their way, heroes giving in to corruption... Those who've grown bored of conventional stories find a guilty pleasure in such things.|While Illustrious is a great teacher during exercises, Indomitable seems hellbent on always cutting corners... Maybe they bore her and all she wants is to go home and chat over tea. Heehee.
touch: Will you say the words, or do you want me to do it? Heehee♪
touch2: You wouldn't hesitate on the battlefield, would you? Go on, show me how brave you are♥
win_mvp: I dedicate this victory to you, my beloved Commander.

battle: If it's for your sake, I suppose I can put in a bit more effort...
detail: Should you run into any problems... You should come to me first, not my sisters... Y-yeah, I think I'm fine with that...
expedition: The commission fleet seems to have come back. Hurry up and go– Err, I mean, let's go greet them together.
feeling5: Let's see, the next things to do on our date are... chilling together indoors, leisurely enjoying some tea, then quietly arrange some flowers. Hm? You want to go outside? I, I think our schedule's already pretty packed. Look, every time we go outside on a date, my legs get all puffy the next day...
home: I pray for the Commander's safe return... Ow, ow, ow... Who thought prayer could be such a painful thing... Oh my, is that you, Commander?
login: Good day, Commander. Umm, uhh... M-maybe there's something I can help you out with?
lose: Don't worry, I'm the type of girl who can bounce right back after a little nap.
main_extra: Commander, did you want to go to the tea party? Um, in that case... Ugh, why is this so hard...|Did you sleep well yesterday? If you're tired, you might want to take a little nap or go on a stroll outside first. touch: I'm serious. Y-you can come see me even if you don't have any problems...
touch2: You're such a bully...
win_mvp: MVP, huh... Darn it, now I'm going to have to rest up to get my motivation back!

detail: Etiquette training does suck, but I'll keep doing my best to become a dependable lady of the Royal Navy! ...Ehehe, this is how I'll hide my true self in front of others so that only the people I really care about get to see the real me! Yep, that's perfect!
expedition: Going out with you to greet the commission team... I know what this is! This is what they call a "grown-up date"! ...It's not?
headtouch: Hawawah! I put so much effort into brushing my hair just right... You'd better get it back to how it was!
home: Commander, come over here! There there, pat pat, good Commander! Hm? Big sis Illustrious taught me this! She said this is the best way to help you relax.
login: Commander! You've finally returned! Did you bring that Iris dessert I said I wanted to try? ...Wow, thank you, Commander!
lose: Urk... Commander, they're bullying meee...
mail: Commander, you've got mail! I brought it right away! Do you have a reward for me?
main_extra: At tea parties, you have to sit straight up and deal with all these dumb, annoying manners... But when I'm with you and my sisters, I can relax! I wish I could always eat tasty foods without a care!|Commander, you know one or two of Her Majesty's secrets, don't you? For example... Maybe she's not all that elegant in private? I promise I won't tell anyone else!|I recently learned about this "rock" genre of music. I rather like it! My sisters say it's not ladylike, but... What about you? Do you like "rock," Commander?
mission: A new mission? If you're going to be busy, then I guess I'll have to pass the time alone... How sad.
mission_complete: Mission complete! Commander, shall we take a break? You look tired, so I'm worried about you...
touch: If you're free right now, then let's have a tea party together! We can leave out all of the boring manners and stuff.
touch2: I-i-i-it is far too soon for me to be participating in such acts!
win_mvp: I won! Look, Commander, I'm in first place!

battle: Behold, Commander! This victory I'll dedicate to you!
feeling5: Never would I have imagined this – that one day I, a loner with no one relying on her, would be mulling over my future together with you. Thank you, for accepting me and giving meaning to my life. You are my greatest love.
home: You've returned. Unscathed, no less. I'm certain you'll welcome me back with those same words, even should I return alone. Truly, that is a comforting sensation.
login: Splendid; you're back. Are you going to hunker down, or take a breather? Whichever the case, I will do the same.
main_extra: You brought meaning to my existence. As a token of my gratitude, I will forever bring you victory.|It will take time to accustom myself to being wed, but as long as you're here, I will never doubt or feel lost.|It's as I feared. Being alone has become unbearable to me. I blame you for this. For... changing me for the better.
touch: Commander, I am glad to serve you.
touch2: Mgh... Give me a moment. I need time to... accustom myself.
win_mvp: See that? I will never let you down.

feeling5: Oh, Owner~! Anywhere you wanna go today? Anything particular you want for dinner? Maybe there's something you wanna say? Ask me, and I'll tell you: I wanna go wherever you're going, I wanna have dinner with and most importantly, I love you, Owner~♡
headtouch: I got my hands on a new set of ears! Try 'em on for size, Owner! Aww, don't be like that! You'd look adorable in them!
home: Weeelcome back, Owner! Are you okay? Did you have any lovey-dovey thoughts about me? Don't be shy to say it, I want to know!
login: Owneeeeeer! Glomp! Squeeze! Cuddle! Sniff! Alright, that should do it for now! Cuddling you has become a part of my daily routine at this point♡
main: nil|Me, spacing out? Nuh-uh! ...Well, I guess I do sometimes when I think about you, my perfect Owner~♡|Do you want tea or some juice, Owner? I personally like the orange juice they sell in vending machines! ...H-hey, just because I like premade stuff doesn't mean I'm lazy!
mission_complete: Mission complete! Total walk in the park for the two of us!
touch2: Owneeeer! Hm? No, I didn't need anything, why? Can't I just touch you outta nowhere if I feel like it?

feeling5: Hm, I see. This is what it feels like to be loved by someone you love. Not wanting to snatch someone away or wanting to monopolize them, but feeling excited and safe... It feels a bit strange...
main: I mean, yes, of course I wanted to improve my artillery and torpedoes, get thicker plating, and improve my engines—but it's too expensive to do so.|nil|How'd you like some lime juice? Yes, I do think fresh juice is the best, and you're gonna need to get used to it when you're sailing the high seas. Hehe~
touch2: Hey... What do you think you're doing while the sun's still up...

battle: What would you have me do, dear Commander?
detail: A pleasure to see you today. As you can see, I am currently partaking in a tea party with my esteemed colleagues. Why don't you join us? Let's find you a seat... How about in my lap?

touch2: I do not condone this, but since you're so insistent... Ohoho.
win_mvp: Now they know the Empire's splendor, and the firmness of our resolves. And you made it possible, Commander.

detail: I'm quite weary myself, so I propose we hold our conversation in the thermae. Hm? Is something the matter? Yes, I am asking you to join me.
expedition: The commission team has returned. Oh, I shall accompany you? I assume you want me to discipline the slackers among– Ah, nothing of the sort. I see.
home: Congratulations on your triumph, Commander. I've determined our next destination. Let us march onward.
login: Now that you're here, let us begin today's tasks.
main_extra: You need some fresh air? Allow me to assist. I can punch a hole through this window with my– Oh, I suppose I'll open it like normal.|When my ambition is one day realized, I shall engrave your name upon my laurel crown. Come that day, I want you present to see this moment with your own eyes.
touch: Kindly make your request to Roma. You need not offer tribute on this occasion.
touch2: How very bold of you... You're becoming more and more like Romulus.

battle: I'm fine, because I have the Commander with me!
detail: I'm glad to have someone to rely on, but I feel bad doing it when the Commander already has so much work to do... Ugghh... I won't work this out myself. Guess I should ask Trento and the girls for advice...
expedition: Commission completed. I'll tally up the rewards for you.
home: You've been out on nonstop sorties lately, haven't you? So here, I sorted your paperwork to make it easier to read. That should extend your break by a solid ten minutes. Heehee.
login: Here's your daily cup of hot milk. Enjoy it, and then let's get to work♪
main_extra: I should probably make some time for just you and me so I can carry on my always-there role model attitude. But... then it's like I'm keeping you all to myself...|Some girls love doting on you, and some love being doted on by you... I'm not sure how to put it, I just feel a little nagged about that...
mission: You have a mission. How about we complete it together for a change of pace?
mission_complete: Mission done and dusted. You're awesome, Commander! Come here for a hug... The rest of you will get one later♪
touch: Yes? Do you want me to pamper you? Heehee.
touch2: Indulge yourself as much as you want♪
win_mvp: Now this is how a role model rolls! Heehee~

battle: Friends, heed my call – Begin our advance!
detail: Let's give this another try... Are you sure it's supposed to work like this? ...Hyah! ...Ohmygosh! It worked! My Commander, Miss Illustrious!
home: My Commander, if you receive any troublesome requests, will you delegate them to me?
login: Please look after me today as well, my Commander~
main: Zzzzz... Ahhn, you mustn't~ Hwuh? My Commander? Hehe~ I wonder why you didn't directly wake me up?
main_extra: This is your favorite food, isn't it~ ...Oh, it's not? But that's what Miss Junyou told me. She's your childhood friend, isn't she...?
mission: Let me handle this task... Oh, are you worried that I won't be able to handle it, my Commander...?
mission_complete: Thank you very much, my Commander! I did a good job, didn't I?
touch2: Oh my... Just what am I going to do with you, my Commander...

detail: Whew, nothing beats a good bath... Huh? What do you mean "what's with the towel"? I just got out of the bath, that's what?
expedition: The commission team's back. I'll go bid them a splendrous ret– Eh, forget it. You're up, Commander.
feeling5: We don't have to do anything today. You heard me – you can be like me and just not do anything productive. And if you do something wild, I'll let it slide.
headtouch: Mhh... That's nice. Do it again.
home: You've returned. I got you something to snack on. How nice of me, right? You may thank me with a headpat.
login: Evening... You're not tired right before work? Darn, I was hoping we could nap together.
lose: I can't let the Commander see me like this... I'm supposed to be brilliant...
mail: A carrier pigeon... I wish I could fly like a bird. A rigging upgrade might make that possible.
main_extra: Littorio! Is dinner ready yet? Don't forget I'm brilliant. I'll starve to death if you take too long.|Need some help with that? ...You can do it on your own? Geesh, soon there'll be nothing left for me to do.|It's nice being a carrier. I don't need to get my hands dirty, all I have to do is pilot my planes. I'm so brilliant for being able to fight on my own.
mission: Missions, hmm? Completing them is key to promoting your brilliance and Sardegna's splendor.
mission_complete: Brought you the mission rewards...! Oof! They're a lot heavier than I expected.
touch: Is dinner ready?! ...Not yet, huh...
touch2: ...I love when you do this♡
win_mvp: I'm brilliant, aren't I? Yeah, I am... Hehehe.

feeling5: Thanks for everything you do, Commander... Hehehehe... Tell you what, I-I'll make you dinner today... Mushroom marinade, mushroom risotto, and my own mushroom special... Hehehehe....
main: I sorted all your paperwork, Commander... Hehehe... C-could I get a "thank you," please...?|nil|I love the dark... Hehehe... It hides you from people who'd judge you...
main_extra: Could I c-come with you on mission briefings? I am your secretary, after all... Hehehe...♡|Helping out with prototype equipment is such a chore... Ugh...
mission: Another mission? O-okay...
touch2: Oh, Commander... Hehe, hehehe...♡
win_mvp: Hehe, hehehehe... S-say something good about me...

battle: I've got a brilliant plan B, so do your worst!
detail: I wanna thank you for always giving me input and listening to my rambling by inventing something that'll be of use to you~ Just tell me whatcha want♡
expedition: Commission rewards are here. Let's check out what we got and see what new things we can come up with!
feeling5: That pillow cover drying in the sun is of course the one with your darling da Vinci in a raunchy pose♡ ...You thought I was serious? So you're saying you WOULD own that... Guess I'll just have to make one♪
home: Good going on that sortie! Feeling beat, don'tcha? Let's fix those stiff shoulders with my massage-o-tron! Have a seat in my lap and just relax♪
login: You're looking alive today, Commander! Heheh, must be thanks to my li'l works-like-charm alarm clock♪
main_extra: Not all ideas are feasible to materialize, but that's no reason not to try! As they say, the proof is in the pudding♪|Commander! I've got another brilliant new invention to... Darn, you're busy. I'll give it a show to Torricelli instead.|I may be a short sleeper, but you need your beauty sleep. I also know what it's like to be in the flow, which is all the more reason why you need to call it a day! Come on, it's time to go to bed, Commander!
mission: It's time to test out my machine that replicates your signature! ...No? Come on, there's no harm in automating that bit!
mission_complete: Mission complete♪ You know what you get for shutting down my brilliant idea? A thorough tickling!
touch: You got an idea outta the blue? Quick, here's a pen and paper – write it down before you forget it!
touch2: Heheh, I knew you were being too modest up to now♪
win_mvp: We won, Commander♡ Heck yeah, that look of surprise is just what I wanted to see~

detail: I don't want to catch those eyes of yours staring at any other girl, Commander. You'll make her get as lost in your heart as I have. We can't have that, because you're mine.
expedition: Let us head out and greet the commission team together.
feeling5: I've thought of a myriad of metaphors for my love for you. A lighthouse out at sea, a guiding star... None of them quite hit home, though. Perhaps I ought to forego such things and just express my unadulterated feelings... I love you. I will always be with you.
headtouch: Hm? Yes, I was thinking of you, too.
home: Have a seat and get comfortable, Commander. I've made you tea and sweets. Indeed – your favorite ones. I've committed them to memory.
login: You're here, Commander. Yes, I didn't get lost today. I suppose what I should say is... I'm waiting for you to invite me on a stroll.
lose: This is far from over.
mail: Would you share the contents of this letter with me? I'm rather... scratch that, just a little curious.
main_extra: I've got the hang of paperwork by now, Commander. You can stop bothering other girls with it and leave it all to me.|Diplomats often dance at balls as part of their work, so allow me to teach you some moves. Yes, place your hands like this... Feel free to place them further down, even.|What's that? You're studying intel on the enemy? I don't see why you'd concern yourself with such a thing. Can't you just beat them down with overwhelming force?|Commander? Oh, it seems my stroll has unexpectedly brought me to your room... Perhaps you could say that's part of the fun of traveling, heehee. What do you think?
mission: Don't worry about those missions. I'll handle them.
mission_complete: Mission complete. I daresay I've grown quite good at this.
touch: I've heard that massages are good for the skin. Incidentally, may I... borrow your hands for a bit?
touch2: I've been taking good care of these as well, by the way!
upgrade: Whatever foes or obstacles come between us, I shall eliminate them all.
win_mvp: My strategy went rather well. It was all thanks to your teachings, Commander.

detail: What are you ogling me for? I don't see what you get out of this...
home: You've earned three cookies for today's sorties. Mm, that'll be all. Now say "aah."
login: You've got all this work to do before the end of the day? ...I guess we just have to make a miracle happen...
lose: Next time, do your job and command properly.
main: nil|nil|Hmh. Just so you know, Gromky, the Commander isn't slacking on the job. Mhm, that's all.
main_extra: You always drink tea with me, so why do you leave all the cookies to me? ...You'd rather I eat all I want? Huh, I see...
mission: Are you ignoring all these missions, hoping they'll go away? Yikes...
touch2: Uhh, woaaaahhhhh...

detail: Why are you staring at me like that? ...Ah! Did you want me to pat your head! ...Huh? That's not it?
home: Comrade Commander, your reward for today's battle is... you can have as many blini as you'd like! Ehehe~
login: Heyy! You can't get up yet! Didn't I tell you to get more rest?
main: Comrade Commander, you mustn't slack off! ...Huh? You want me to come relax with you? I, I guess I can't get mad at that... Wait, hey! Get back to work!|nil|nil
win_mvp: You've worked real hard, haven't you? Good job, good job~!

battle: Brutes like you deserve brutish answers – punches!
detail: WHAT?! Dust is upon us! Comrade, open the window at once! Or else your screens will be ruined!
feeling5: You needn't worry, Comrade! I may be obsessed with machinery, but I could never forget about you, my dear lover! On that note, why don't we go on a date to that toy store which opened just today? It supposedly has tons of mechanical toys on offer!
home: Allow me to fix up your escort ship, Comrade! While I'm at it, do you want any new additions? Like a massage chair, for instance.
login: Welcome back, Comrade! Oh, mind your step around the components on the floor! Without really thinking, I turned your office into a second workshop. Hah-ha-ha-haah!
main_extra: The grinding of gears, the whizzing of a propeller, the ringing that tickles my heart... Whuh?! Hey! What are you touching me for, Comrade?!|Another one of plastic's shortcomings is the difficulty in fixing it. How so? Well, if I were to WHACK it, it would simply break – unlike metal.|Comrade! What are your thoughts on the Soobrazitelny-brand Automatic Door Closer? Now you'll never need to close the door manually again! I'll fix the frame damage caused during installation later!
mission: We have new missions! Comrade! With me by your side, you have nothing to fear!
mission_complete: With your commanding and my ingenuity, we could finish these missions with our eyes closed!
touch: Whereas metal is tough and sleek, your touch is soft and calming.
touch2: Fweh?!
win_mvp: Success! Hoh-ha-ha-hah! Victory for the galaxy-brained mechanic!

battle: Just have to fight... Everything will go fine!
detail: Are you free, Commander? I could... kill some time. Are you fine with hanging out?
expedition: Our commission comrades are back. They told me about some interesting things they saw... Do you wanna know, Commander?
feeling5: I want to be the only one for you. Of all the girls close to you, I want to be your most faithful one. When you look at all of us, I want to be the only one you really see... That's fine, right?
home: You're back by my side again... Phew. Now I feel fine.
login: I will always be right here, waiting for you, Commander. You're fine with that, I hope?
lose: Please never leave me behind. I promise I will keep you safe.
main_extra: Huff, puff... There... I wrote your name and mine in the fog on the window. This looks fine, right?|I never wanna become a cactus. If I could grow in spite of neglect, then I worry people would actually abandon me...
mission: New missions... They're not so tough when I have you.
mission_complete: Are you... gonna go claim the mission rewards? Would it be fine if I went with you?
touch2: Umm... (*blushes*)

feeling5: Isn't it nice to just huddle together quietly and do nothing sometimes? ...You don't want to bore me? It's not boring! I'm never bored when I'm with you!
headtouch: Hmph... You'll have to style my hair into something cute later!
home: Way to go, Commander! You can have a hug as a reward! ...Did that make your fatigue go away? That's great, heehee!
login: Commander! I missed you... It was lonely without you, but I stayed positive and waited for you.
lose: I will protect you, Commander! Retreat, now!
main_extra: Hold still for a minute, Commander! I'm going to put a ribbon on you! ...It's over-the-top cute, so it doesn't fit you? Don't say that! Everything cute looks best on you!|I've finished all the paperwork now! Is there anything else I can help you with? ...I'm free to do whatever I want? Okay, then I'll wait for you right here! I want to spend more time with you, heehee!|Commander, Commander! Can I put up more decorations around the office? ...You're sure? Hooray! But I'm not allowed to decorate you? Aww! But you'd look so good covered in cute stuff!
mission: Commander! We've been informed of a new mission! I can help you finish it before you know it!
mission_complete: The mission rewards list checks out! Please put a cute checkmark here!
touch: Hm? Are you giving me this ornament? Wooow! It's sooo cute!
touch2: Here and now? You're awfully bold today, Commander!

expedition: Hm? The commission team's back. Aren'tcha gonna go meet 'em?
feeling5: When we're apart, I feel like I have to push myself endlessly to prove my strength, to prove my value... "Like pulling back a bow's string too hard"? Yeah, something like that... I really don't know how I'd manage if you weren't here.
headtouch: If ya like touching me... then fine, I-I'll let you!
home: Look who's back. You did a killer job out there! And not even a scratch! Heehee!
login: Welcome back. Nice, you're lookin' full of life today!
main_extra: The time has come to unveil the graffiti master's latest work! Whaddya think? Ain't it the cutest thing you've ever seen? Heehee, I knew you'd like it♪|You're glad I've been pullin' fewer all-nighters lately? Yeah, 'cuz... You keep complimenting me for my hard work, so I feel I can relax and have fun for a bit too...|Ah... Achoo! Would you PLEASE turn up the temp on the AC, Commander?!
mission: You've got a new mission! Let's do it together!
touch2: Whoa, whoa! We're in public! Wh-wh-what the hell are you thinkin'?!

detail: You wanna know more about the war I fought so hard in, darling? Heheh! Maybe I should brief you then~ Not that I have to, someone else can tell you of my exploits.
feeling5: I may look young, but I've got a rich history and a vast repertoire of knowledge, which is how I know your mind like the back of my hand, darling♪ "Wisdom really comes with age"... We're not touching that topic! Ever! That has nothing to do with it, stupid!
login: So, what are we starting the day with, darling? ♪
main: Secretary work, huh... I'll do it if you can beat me at a game. Although you have any chance of winning anyway♪|Mh...! I think I just strained my back... N-no, I didn't say anything!|nil
touch2: You love it when they're big, don'tcha? And I love you

battle: Полный ход!
detail: Commander, are you hungry? Well, you'll just have to wait. Once I say 'okay,' then you can eat.
feeling5: Still feeling a little uneasy? Just wait a bit longer. You need to stay bound to me like this for now, but sooner or later you won't have to think anymore, you won't have to worry, and you can forget all that pain.
home: You did so well on that sortie... Now you just let me take care of everything.
login: Welcome, Commander. Time for another day of hard work. By the way... Have you been wearing your bridle like we talked about?
main: Commander, what's wrong? I'm here, and I'm not going anywhere.|It's a big responsibility to have someone trust you so much. But don't worry, I'm holding your reins tightly.|Just let me know when you'd like to talk to another girl. You'd be very embarrassed to be seen like this, hm? Hehe, I think it's fine if somebody sees, actually.
touch: Hehe, I think I want to touch you too, Commander.
touch2: Hehe, I'll join you in a minute, okay?
win_mvp: Hehehe, I'm happy if you are.

home: One's individual leadership abilities are hardly as important as the will to stand side-by-side with one's comrades. In this regard, you have excelled without a doubt.
login: What's on the itinerary today? If there's anything that requires me to uplift the spirits of our comrades, I'm all in!
main_extra: ...Having that said, it isn't inconceivable that war devolves into attrition. In such cases, we must be able to adapt to changes...|Let me tell you this— never underestimate the eyes and ears of the Northern Parliament!
touch2: Hmm... I would like you to be a bit more mindful of the rules.

battle: The Commander is watching! All shipgirls, with me!
detail: Ouch! Sorry for making you wrap these bandages for me... Don't worry about me. It's better if we go all-out during these exercises. I'm used to this, anyway.
feeling5: Solving your problems and warming your bed are both my responsibilities... Haha! I'm kidding. I do it all because I want to, after all. Oh? That's not what you expected the punchline to be? Well...
headtouch: I'm fine... Oh, that's not why you're touching me? H-heheh... My mistake.
home: Commander, over here! You're finally back. Come enjoy some piping-hot borscht.
login: Phew... Commander? Did you turn the AC on? Th-thank you...
lose: ...We mustn't retreat! Ours is the final line of defense!
main_extra: Is something on your mind? I could... Oh. You say you're just daydreaming? I see... *sigh*|Back straight! Fix that posture! Head up! Heehee, there! Now this feels more like an outing.|*blows*... Ack! I forgot to move the tea out of the thermos... O-oh, ignore me! I don't burn that easily, I swear, haha...
mission_complete: This is a rather paltry reward... Perhaps I should look into this?
touch: Is this a distress signal from our poor, dependable Commander? Heehee~!
touch2: Your hands are so warm, Commander...
win_mvp: Such a passionate celebration. It's beyond warm—why, I'd call it downright fiery! Heehee.

login: Good morning! I managed to make it on time today. Teehee~♪
main_extra: A friend told me a while ago that being around me feels warming sometimes, and chilling other times... Umm, that's not really a good thing, is it?|Staaare... Hey~♡ You're really good-looking, Commander~♪
touch2: Gosh, your hand feels so warm~

feeling5: Dates must be planned as thoroughly as a battle. These three should do... "Port Dates and You," "Top 100 Dating Techniques," and "How to Steal the Commander's Heart on a Date." ...Oh? You say I should leave the planning to you? I-if you say so...
headtouch: I don't... quite understand... *blushes*
home: Ah, Comrade Commander. I was so focused on work that I didn't notice your return. I would've liked to give you a more special welcome, but I lost track of time... Sorry.
login: Welcome back, Comrade Commander. You think I shouldn't wait for you all the time? ...It's okay. I was looking forward to seeing you.
main_extra: Do you still think I'm as cold as ice? Haha, well, that ice melted long ago thanks to you.|Kirov told me that if I want something, I should be bold. I understand that logically, but shouldn't I be more careful when it comes to emotions? I mean, this is my first time, so...|I'd always thought that absence is what makes the heart grow fonder. But staying so close to you and chatting... Heehee, it's pretty nice.
touch: Your hands are cold... Would you like me to warm them up?
touch2: We should both be more straightforward... *blushes*

home: Do you really think this is all it takes to satisfy everyone? Exactly. Let that annoyance motivate you to do better.
login: Hats off to you for clocking in on time. See? You can do it if you just try. Hehehe.
main: Have you checked out that report yet? ...If you've got time to make excuses, you've got time to do your job.|nil|nil
main_extra: Maybe I should put a collar on you, like Chapayev suggested... What? Nothing important. Focus on your work.|Do your job well, and you'll be rewarded. Use your head and think up something good, then I'll see what I can do. Hehehe~
touch: You're in need of some guidance, aren't you?
touch2: Hehehe. You know what? I'll let you have your fun for once.

detail: Here to see me? 'kay. No need to cover my tracks... Truth is, I wanted to see you too.
headtouch: If you really must...
home: *sniff*... I smell gunpowder on you, but not blood. Good to know you're unharmed.
login: Welcome back. What are we doing today? Work, first of all? Fine. I'll wait here in the meanwhile.
main_extra: I do things my way... but if need be, I'll follow your commands. I trust your better judgment.|The Northern Parliament's having a party? I don't mind liquor, it's just... Ah, forget it. I'll go, if only to make you look good. When it's time for chitchat, back me up.|Those white tundras and snowy valleys still hold a special place in my heart. I'd happily take you with me to see them sometime.
mission: You've got new missions. I'll help you... in the way I know best.
mission_complete: Mission complete. Hah, we're starting to look like a team.
touch: I'm right here. I'm bad at reading emotions, so if you need something, just say it.
touch2: It's time I taught you who's the hunter and who's the prey.

main: Comrade~ have a bit more to drink~ That Marat can't keep up with me~ C'mon, keep me company until dawn.|nil|No strong enemies around? I feel your frustration, comrade... Well then, come at me. Let's make life worth living!
touch: I see, I see, so you want to fully grasp the extent of my rigging. Very well! I have no objections, for your courage is commendable as well!
touch2: You are forgiven, comrade! Such courage deserves to be rewarded! Come, put your hands all over me until you've had your fill!

expedition: The commission team has returned. Let's go bid them welcome back, shall we? I'll... try, for their sake.
feeling5: Oh, dear... Looking back at it, "deepen our relationship" was an outrageous thing to say. Then you said all those things and even threw a wedding... Thinking about it now... it makes my cheeks warm.
home: Good, you're back, Comrade Commander. Now let's have a break. A healthy body leads to improved productivity.
login: Mh... Looks like you're in good shape as well, Comrade Commander.
main_extra: Our path is one towards a bright future. It doesn't matter how rugged or long the journey is, because the many sights we'll see along the way will become wonderful memories.|...You think I should smile when speaking to someone to not make them anxious? Not a bad idea... Like this, then?|I'd like to thank you once more, Comrade Commander. I've never felt better than I do when I'm by your side... Hm? You liked my smile just now? I... see...|I make endearing faces when I look at Arctic hares? You really think so? Oh, dear...
touch2: You like doing it here, do you? Mmh... I don't mind it at all. Heehee.
win_mvp: Follow the plan and seize victory!

expedition: What, you wanna bet on whether or not our commission fleet is bringing back a big haul? Nah, no need for that. We pretty much know the outcome already.
home: There is no harm in prolonging the suffering of our foes, but do not forget the reason why we are here, Comrade.
login: You've come, Comrade. As punctual as always.
mail: Letters, huh? Let's take a look... Wouldn't want to miss out on anything juicy.
main_extra: That's checkmate. Hey hey, throwing in the towel already? What, you're making it seem like I'm bullying you or something~|The port sure is peaceful... just as it should be. Violence should have no place outside the battlefield.
mission_complete: All right. After we finish these missions, you should go back to pursuing your own ambitions.
touch2: Hey, hey... I didn't call you here to make you all hot and bothered.

detail: This port has such abundance. That leaves me one core duty. I must bring emotional enrichment to your life.
home: Comrade Commander, please eat this. Think nothing of it. Call it a personal supplement.
main: I need only focus my attentions on battle? That is a reasonable decision... But does it mean my clerical skills did not pass muster?|nil|nil
touch: Comrade Commander, today's handshake. Mmm. Let us properly follow proper protocols today.
touch2: Is this what the Iris would call a "breach of etiquette?"

detail: With you commanding even in the field, and me offering advice on the fleet's course – yes, the port has a bright future ahead of it. Hehehe~
feeling5: Would you please tell me ahead of time when you want me to switch from soldier to lady mode? It's hard to dote on you at the drop of a hat – I'm not used to that. As an aside, would you like to go on a date? ...Hehehe. Expect me to make the first move for as long as I'm not used to doting on you.
home: Results look good, same with the after-action report... And you, Commander? Good to hear! ...Mmm, this tea came out excellent, even by my high standards.
login: Attention: the Commander is back! Now then, what's our first task of the day?
main_extra: That's hardly a drink suited for a tea party, Belorussiya... And Rossiya! That's not the right way to use that! Sorry, Commander, my hands are a bit tied for the moment!|How my abilities are put to use is for you to determine. I have no doubt you'll make the right call.
mission: Attention: new missions have come in. I suggest taking a gander at them.
mission_complete: Mission complete! That's created some time for us to go on a date.
touch: Need advice? I can offer mine only if you'll rely on me!
touch2: I'm not sure what to say about this...

detail: My, Comrade Commander? Did you come to see me because you wanted an invitation to our drinking party, or officially, "tea" party? I've already slipped one into your office drawer~♪
home: I brought some beer! Heh, unlike Gangut, you'd get bored of only drinking vodka pretty fast, right?
login: Good day, Comrade Commander. Revolution isn't all fun and games. Can I trust you to guide us all to battle once more?
main_extra: I'd look miserable if I got drunk at work. Listen! You'd better stop me before I get drunk! ...Cheers!|Aww, someone looks like they're ready to learn. Okay! Sevastopol, dreadnought and training ship, would be happy to teach you!|There is no end to revolution. Rest easy; you will forever be my Comrade Commander.
touch: Ask me for anything. As a comrade, I intend to do everything in my power to help you.
touch2: C-Comrade Commander... What was the point of that, exactly?

detail: Oh, do you want to play with Pirozhki, too? Heehee, sorry, but no. You have your work to deal with – namely, figuring out the cost of the Ganguts' drinking party♪
expedition: Ah, the girls who went on a commission are back already. You're linked not just with me, but with them as well. Heehee.
home: Way to go, sweetheart. Go on, sit down and let me take care of you. Who's my little soldier? Heehee, yes, you are.
login: Well, hello, sweetheart. I love to relax as much as you, but you're supposed to be working right now. Please be mindful, lest you get on other girls' nerves♪
main_extra: No need to be on your best behavior, sweetheart. There's nobody around♡|Go drinking? Sweetheart, please, do you think I'm the same as Sevastopol? ...Heehee, too late to pull out now. You're going to learn just how much we Parliamentarians can guzzle.
touch: This isn't the chain that binds you... THIS is♡
touch2: Heehee... I know you're trying to provoke me into something, sweetheart♡
