login: Good morning. Um, today... there are no lessons planned, right...?
mail: ... (Am I imagining things, or is the work piling up the more I do it...?)
main: Idols shouldn't get too close to their fans, right? So that means I don't have to do these autograph events either. Sweet~♪|If I just stay awake through this lesson, I'll get to enjoy Dunkerque's sweets afterwards... Focus, focus!|Graf Spee wants to rehearse with me? Uh... O-of course I have no issues with that?
mission: Uh, so today's offers are... Ah, wait, nobody said you had to go and accept ALL of them!
mission_complete: Too tired... can't do this anymore... Lemme go to sleep after you look over the rewards!
touch: Ahh~ Yeah, yeah, that's the spot. Keep massaging right there~
touch2: Too tired... I'm gonna die... Ahhh... Waaah...
win_mvp: Long live the glory of the Iris! Rejoice! Weep! ...Wait, I don't need an encore!

battle: We shall efface all that stands in the Commander's path!
detail: Rest assured! If you're approached by any miscreants intent on disrespect, I will scare them off with my lance! Hahaha!
feeling5: My creed says I "must be ready to sacrifice everything for love, even my life." I would never betray you, but I don't know how to martyr myself for love... I needn't do anything so extreme, you say? Hmph, then I implore you to tell me what I SHOULD do! ...A-a date, for starters?!
headtouch: Well, um... Do as you please. Ooohhh... H-h-hey! I didn't tell you to stop!
home: With one as elegant and excellent as you at the helm, I assume your battle went well! I expect no less from the one who guides my sword!
login: Get your act together and learn to clock in early like me! I w-worry about you when you're not around, you know!
main_extra: Resting to regain one's strength is crucial, you say... Ah! Now I see the profound reason for why Le Malin is always doing that!|Whew... Huff... Puff... Your proud Templar Knight has put in a lot of work today! T-tell me you appreciate me already!|Your sword is always at your side! Give me your orders, and I shall carry them out!
mission: Hahah! In times when missions have you overwhelmed, what you should do is call upon your sword – that is to say, me!
mission_complete: Mission complete! Don't forget to hand down a few rewards in accordance with who worked hardest!
touch2: St-st-stop it with this caprice!
win_mvp: Hmph! See? I am your most commendable champion!

feeling5: When I think about the time I confessed to you without even knowing it, my face gets all hot... but as long as I can convey this feeling of love, it doesn't matter how hot it gets...
home: Whoa... Simply incredible, Commander! I must follow your example and become a sharper blade!
login: Commander, y-you've come! Is there anything I can d-do for you? A massage, for instance... I'll give it my all!
main_extra: You may say I can loosen up around you, but I fear then I'd turn into a lazy blob... Maybe not being a Chevalier for just a moment is fine. Yeah!|B-being short or tall neither has any bearing on your strength, nor does it determine if you can become a Chevalier! ...Am I really that short?|You'd like to swing my sword? Certainly. You hold it like this... then do this... Whoa! Be careful!
touch: Are you feeling lonesome?
touch2: S-so I hold you tight just like this? ...Am I doing it right?

detail: You wanna know about "that" work? How do I say this... Let's just call it the "Inquisition?" What it means is... Hmm, I really can't tell you after all~♪
home: There's not too much of "that" kind of work to do at this port, huh... Well, as long as the Iris girls are safe and sound here, then I can have fun without worrying about anything! Hehehe!
login: What are we doing today? Why don't you gimme something to do before I turn to rust?
main: nil|♪～Hey Commander, can you help me check if I sharpened this enough? I'm always afraid that I missed a spot or something...|Gotta say, I still prefer working under Jean Bart rather than Algérie. Y'know, it's that whole "don't worry about anything other than slaughtering your enemies" kind of feeling...
touch2: Hm? Hmmmmm? ...Mmm... Well, whatever~♪

feeling5: For someone like me who knows nothing outside of battle, being able to experience so many different things... makes me truly happy whenever we do things together, Commander. Might this be... true love?
home: Commander, how are you able to inspire our friends to such an extent? Every time we go on a sortie, I find myself thinking about it.
login: Welcome back, Commander. I've already prepared the tea... Huh? Wasn't I supposed to pour the leaves into the cup? I thought it would be best to fill it up as much as possible...
mail: So, it's possible to open the letter without using my blade after all... I understand now.
main_extra: Affixing your stamp here signifies your approval, right? In that case... Umm, does multiple stamps signify strong approval?|If we were to further retrofit this rigging and amplify the volume... Alright, let's give it a try right now!
touch: You want me to fold you within my wings...?
touch2: I don't quite understand, but... if it pleases you, that makes me glad...

expedition: Our supplies have arrived. Don't worry, I've already checked up on them myself!
feeling5: Commander, did you have any plans for the evening? Ahaha, it's nothing special. I was just thinking that I'd like to eat dinner with you tonight. The reason is... Well, isn't wanting to spend more time with you reason enough? Haha~♪
home: Do you need some help with the reports? Leave them to me, and go take a break. I'll find you if I need anything from you.
login: Commander, the documents for you to take care of today are on your desk. ...No need to look so down, Commander~ I'll help you with anything!
lose: What a miscalculation... I'm sorry, Commander...
main_extra: Algérie invited you to a cat café? Haha, then let's go there after we're done with work.|I'll help you out so you don't need to work extra hours.|If someone wants to disturb the peace that we've built... Well, it's our job to stop them, isn't it?
mission_complete: I've gone and collected the mission rewards for you. This favor's on the house~♪
touch: If you want me to pamper you, just say the word~♪
touch2: Commander? What might you be thinking about?
win_mvp: Yep~ Feel free to keep relying on me~♪

detail: Oh, Commander. ...Next time I'm off duty, I'm planning on checking out a sushi train with Dunkerque. Of course, you're welcome to join me. Hehehe.
feeling5: Love, how are the plans for our next date looking? Oh, I know that the destination's basically decided upon. More than that, I was thinking things like... where we'll eat dinner, or where we'll stay. We have to plan out everything carefully so we can enjoy the date that much more!
headtouch: My my, do you want to be pampered like a child today?
home: You look really tired... Darling, you shouldn't push yourself too hard. Please, leave this to me and go lie down for a bit.
login: Welcome back, dear. What will you start working on first?
lose: Oh no, I lost... I'm sorry for letting you down...
mail: Dear, you've got some new mail. I wonder if I should try my hand at writing some love letters myself. Hehehe.
main: nil|Commander, is there anything you'd like for dinner today? Something other than dinner...? Oh my, how bold~ ...That's something you can look forward to later♪|Whether it's during work or in your daily life, it's no good to be too strict on yourself. Make sure you rest properly when you have the time, alright?|Hmm~ How is this one thiiiis cute... That's right. I'll have to show this to Miss Richelieu next time. Hehehe~. |nil
mission: We've just received a new directive from the higher-ups. Oh? It seems that you're just as busy as always... As much as I'd like to do some of this work in your stead, I suppose I wouldn't be able to?
touch2: There's no reason to be so impatient, right? Hehehe♡

detail: (Huh? What is this about a "forced no-overtime day"?! Commander, you bully... Tch... But if that's what it takes for us to get our date... then I'll just have to deal with it!)
feeling5: This time, it's definitely perfect... I'm alone with the Commander, and my winning gear is ready... Yeah. I'm basically invincible!
home: Welcome back, Commander. You're on a break right now, but get this – so am I. I-in other words, umm... You get what I want to say, right?
login: I organized your files in order of priority before you came here. A-and if you're free after work, we could go somewhere... M-maybe?
main_extra: You'd be surprised how many fields I work in. Heheh, the eve of battle... The sunken Alma... If you'd like to see my movie, Commander, why don't we make it a date?|Holy duties... Wait, we're all done with them?! Hooray! Now... Huh? It's already dawn! Th-then how about we take a walk and watch the sunrise...?|Achoo! Chilly... Huh? You'll warm me up? Heehee, you really are warm, Commander♡
touch: With you around, I hardly need pillows. Ah, paradise...
touch2: Commander... You don't think my proportions are weird, do you?

expedition: Commission complete. Yesss! ...Well, Commander? Is there any praise coming?
feeling5: I was always a woman who was anxious and acting tough – until you came along and changed me completely. I'm going to hold on to you tightly, hog all your attention, and make you never choose anyone else over me. This is my crime, and it is your punishment... because I'm now the happiest woman in the world.
home: You've kept me waiting for far longer than is reasonable, Commander. You better be ready to make up for how much I missed you. Come, we're going to the music room.
login: Hello, Commander. I've already gotten started on the work. Don't worry, I can do this all by myself today – that's how used to it I've gotten now♪
main_extra: Commander. Hey, Commaaander. What are you thinking about? It better not be anything except work and me. Or else...♥|Dunkerque's desserts... Mmm... I can't stop eating them. Makes me want to do nothing but eat them together with you all day.|Why don't we visit the music room after work is over? I'll "play you a song" nobody else nobody else gets to hear♥
mission: You have new missions. The more of them pile up, the more you'll need my help, right?
mission_complete: Mission complete. Wonderful – like the freshness and comfort of a newly baked dessert.
touch: I do like this, so don't be afraid to go even bolder, Com~man~der♥
touch2: You look VERY content. Good. Now stay focused on me♡
win_mvp: I'd looove some dessert as a treat. Heehee. Make it extra delicious this time, please.

battle: All hail the Vichya Dominion!
detail: I'm not the kinda girl who goes shopping with Dunkerque and Algérie. But you knew that already, being the person who knows me best, right? On the other hand, I wouldn't mind doing that with you.
expedition: Guess that merrymaking team's come back.
feeling5: ...Oh, crap, guess I dozed off. How 'bout you take a quick nap too? You could use my lap for a headrest. Take it easy. You and I, we're always by each other's side.
home: I mighta once had a big role to play, but with you in command, I just never get to truly act.
login: Gimme that, I'm gonna help ya out... Of course I'm gonna assist, I'm your secretary.
main: I ain't letting any new talent outshine me. I am Jean Bart, the Vichya Dominion's most powerful ship and bearer of the sacred Iris' name. This title is my pride, and I will never surrender it.|If you wanna go talk to Richelieu then I could come with ya. We believe in different things, but we're still sisters.|Praying isn't my thing, but wishing is fine by me. 'Cause wishing for the wellbeing of the one you love is what it means to be human.
mission: This loot ain't nearly good enough. Not for me, nor for you.
touch: Look, just don't get too flirty with me...
touch2: You're really that keen on my body?

feeling5: Shhh–– Just take my hand, and come with me. Where to? Naturally, a place free from the prying eyes of others, where we can be our true selves. Look– even though you have your doubts about me, you're still coming along. In other words, that's proof that you trust me, right?
home: Let's try exploring other possibilities from the last operation a bit more thoroughly. Will you play the role of the enemy, or shall I do it?
login: Oh, right on time. To be honest, I wanted to see what you're like when you're late and scrambling to get here... Just for curiosity's sake, of course. Heehee~
lose: An enemy capable of outwitting both Clemenceau and the Commander at the same time? How interesting... Surely you're not going to let this one slide, are you?
mail: Rumor has it that when some of the girls are coming by to deliver your mail, they're also sneaking in some personal effects– Haha, forget I said anything~
main_extra: "Clemenceau, that wicked woman. She somehow managed to snatch the Commander away from right under our noses..." Oh my, I didn't realize there were such outrageous rumors going around already. Heehee, it would appear that I'm not able to fly under the radar anymore.|Heehee, I wonder why you're spacing out all of a sudden~? Are you thinking about your other allies... or about some other girl~?|Richelieu, I thoroughly enjoyed the cat café you recommended to me the other day. Why yes, of course the Commander was with me. You know what they say about good company, don't you? Heehee~
touch: The relationship between the two of us doesn't need to be so stiff and formal, you know? Unless... you're afraid that I'm going to do something to you? Heehee~
touch2: Don't forget this– the more "sins" you commit, the more you will have to "repent"~♪

detail: Information request: Master, how do you like my singing?
expedition: Would you mind if I headed to the harbor and sang a song for the commission team?
feeling5: I completely understand what it means to be an idol now. It's about using my abilities to their fullest to sing brilliant, emotionally touching songs to the world. "Thank you," Master.
home: Master, I just finished a lesson, and... was wondering if we could enjoy a little chat?
login: To do: vocals, dancing, and band aesthetics. Master, what I should I focus on today...?
mail: Master, I'd like your opinion on my participation in this contest...
main: Concept in memory detailed as "saving the world by singing" detected. Is such a thing possible, even for me, Master?|Emotion-packed singing was assessed to be effective at touching Master's heart... Master, won't you... listen to my song?|Promotional materials' claim of me being "inexpressive" are... likely not accurate. I am like everyone else; I want to sing with a bright smile.
mission: Between a photoshoot, performance, or radio show, which should I focus on today, Master?
mission_complete: Report: working as an idol has improved my capabilities. Nice!
touch: I'm practicing at the moment... Do you need something, Master?
touch2: Comet told me that people shouldn't readily get to touch idols... Master, does this qualify as sexual harassment?

battle: Accept this divine punishment.
detail: Are you curious about the Sacrament of Love? Of course, I don't mind sharing with you—In order to make it easier for you to understand, why don't we go on a date?
home: There is no need to fret. I am very well aware that all your battles are magnificent. What need is there for me to pass judgment?
login: Commander, let us pray together. I got up two hours late just to match you.
main_extra: The Independence-class... I don't think those girls understand the Holy Iris's will, but they sure fight well.|While I may no longer hold the qualification to pass judgment upon you, I am still qualified to continue observing your actions. That's the duty of a secretary ship, after all. Hehehe.
mission: Whether or not I pass judgment upon you depends on your progress... Just kidding, of course. Let's work at a reasonable pace.
touch: What is it? Did you need something from me?
touch2: Hehehe...

detail: Analyzing armaments... Condition: satisfactory. Please inform me if you have any orders, Master.
expedition: Attention: confirmation required for commission team's return. Whew...
feeling5: I've studied many emotions, worries, and hopes during my time in this fleet... Now I finally understand what you expect of me, Master. Thank you so, so much, Master...
home: Here is a glass of armagnac, if you'd like.
login: Identification complete. Welcome back, Master!
mail: Attention: confirmation required for new mail. A-ahem!
main: "Raise the corners of your lips"... Executing order. L-like this...? I may be doing it wrong...|Analysis complete. Master is in a state of "slacking off." Slacking off is not good.|"Do whatever you want"... Master, how am I meant to do "whatever"...?|Discrepancy detected between the information in my core and the members of the fleet. Why does everyone smile?
mission: Attention: confirmation required for incomplete missions. Master...?
mission_complete: Attention: confirmation required for mission rewards. Wow...!
touch: I'm waiting for any order you may have, Master.
touch2: Body temperature abnormality detected. Master, what's happening to me...?

detail: Permission to inspect me...? R-right now...?
home: I have prepared us some water and food... Would you like some, Master?
login: Welcome back, Master. I'm attempting to do "whatever I want"...
main: The summer winds... Master, is this what "relaxation" feels like...?|This crab seems to be saying "hello, I'm a crab!" ...Does what I said work as a "joke"?|"Let's go for a swim" – I'll go get a swimg ring... Master, are you sure I "don't need one"?
touch: Your gaze makes me feel odd, Master...
touch2: I'm sorry, Master... My body feels strangely warm...
unlock: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Master, what things do you do to "have fun on the beach"...?

battle: For victory, and for the one I love!
detail: What else do I want to do...? Is there anything the two of us can do other than "play"? If I want to try doing everything, will you be okay with that...?
expedition: A new commission has just been completed. I shall now go greet my companions. Commander, if you have time to spare, do you think we could...
feeling5: You want me to tell you everything I want to do, and everything I don't want to do...? Very well, I promise. In that case, could you tell me what you want, Commander? I want to learn more about you, and experience more things with you...
headtouch: That feels so good...
home: I've been waiting for you all this time. I've wanted to see you... even if for no particular reason...
hp_warning: I can't let things end here, the Commander is waiting for me...!
login: Commander, what are you going to do today? I promised to try to help you today...
lose: I have become soft and weak. Commander, I was afraid I'd never see you again, so I ran away... I'm so sorry...
mail: Commander, I've come to deliver the mail. Is it okay that I'm a bit late...?
main_extra: My free will, and the things I hold dear to me... Yes, I wish to give more of myself for you, and for this port. That is my will.|You wish for me to be the bird that flies freely, not one that is confined to a cage... Even if that bird wishes to remain at your side, you can allow that, right?|Playing with friends makes me feel good. But it's a different kind of good feeling compared to when I'm playing with you... The "good feeling" I get from you is special...
mission: Commander, can you leave this mission to me? You look rather tired, so please rest up for now.
mission_complete: Mission complete. If you think I did a good job, then... could you please praise me?
skill: I won't let you have your way...!
touch: So warm... I want to keep holding on to your hand, now and forever...
touch2: I shall offer you all that I am. That is my will, Commander...
win_mvp: I am victorious. If it is not too much to ask, Commander, I would like a reward from you...

battle: Those who do the most work get the biggest cut!
login: Look who's back! Let's team up and get this paperwork done lightning-quick!
mail: Here's a letter for you! And no, it's not a wanted list. But if you did become an outlaw, you can always flee to some barren corner of the earth.
main_extra: Port law article four! Be good and switch off the light before going to bed! Which means no worky-work either! Nighttime means leisure time!|While I do hate gambling, I'm not opposed to making bets. On that note, I bet I can win your heart with just one single date! Wanna find out?|Booze? God no! Just taking a whiff of that stuff makes my head spin, and drinking it leaves me out cold until morning... In other words, keep it away from me.|I'd like one small favour from you, Commander... That you don't pull an all-nighter! Back in the day when curfews were in place, people got on just fine, didn't they? So, absolutely no staying up late tonight! Got it?
mission_complete: Mission complete! When it comes to my cut... I don't need material stuff, just some break time to smell the roses!
touch: If you're on board with it, we can make up some quick excuse and get out of here right now... Come on, you still don't have the courage?
touch2: L-look, even I shy away from some stuff...
win_mvp: Commander, I trust you to divvy up our booty!

home: Welcome back. It's time for your routine examination... Good, you look fine.
login: There you are. Bask in the glory of the golden light... Um, all I wanted to say is, "welcome back."
lose: No need to put on appearances in front of you, I suppose...
mail: Let us both read your latest letter.
main_extra: I've been receiving fruits and vegetables from my friends around the port, surely as offerings to the Invincible Armada... They're just "worried I'll go hungry otherwise"? That can't be true!|When the going gets too tough, don't push yourself – come to me for help. That is what you preached to me, and now I am preaching it to you.|Fan you with my wings to cool you down? That is not what they're meant for! But, if you want me to give it a try... There, how's that?
touch: I could use a hand with grooming my wings.
touch2: This stirring in my chest... tell me, what is it?

battle: It's too late once I've caught you~♡
detail: *squish squish* My darling Commander, do you like my tentacle massage combined with... Heehee, goodness, I don't know what this is called♡ Will you tell me? Surely you would know~?
feeling5: I'm puzzled. I've done it with you so, so many times, yet I still need so much more... Even now, I'm having dirty thoughts while just standing next to you... Heehee♪ My little ones might snap and cover you in ooze, so if that happens, please don't get mad♡
home: How do you like this~? Heehee, how careless of you to be caught by my tentacles as soon as you come back~ Just relax and I'll make you feel better♡
login: Ohh♡ You bumped into me while trying to avoid my tentacles, hmm? Heehee, there's no escaping me~ Your body belongs to me, my darling Commander♡
main_extra: Quiet, quiet... Heehee, oh, my darling~ My little ones can't help but get fidgety whenever you're around♡|My most prized possession? Oh, my darling, you are too good at feigning ignorance... It's your body, your soul, your stories – I always look forward to them♡|I have a one-of-a-kind advantage when it comes to concerts – I can play the whole orchestra using my tentacles~ Now, I dedicate this next performance to my darling Commander♪|
touch: My little ones are easier to follow than me, you say? Heehee, I suggest that you don't test my patience~ Tease me too much, and I might just suck you dry, my darling Commander~♡
touch2: Do you want to feel my little ones' embrace? Or maybe... Heehee~ Come here~ I'll satisfy your every desire~♡
win_mvp: You're going to rot, rust, and corrode anyway, so why not become a part of my collection? Heehee♡

battle: May the storm take you!
detail: Teach you how to turn invisible like me? It's... not something you can learn. Putting aside whether you can or can't, how am I supposed to be by your side if I can't see you? Heh.
expedition: You'll draw their attention, and I'll appear from behind and spook 'em. Alright! We've got a plan!
feeling5: Shh. I know it's just you and me here, but you don't want anyone to hear us, do you? While I can always vanish from sight if someone shows up, you can't. That's why you have to be quiet. Same goes for me.
headtouch: You... like the curvature of my horns? Didn't think you'd care about them... Now I'm a li'l self-conscious... *blushes*
home: Feel like you're on fire after that last battle? Hahahah! That's where I come in. C'mere and cool your face in my chest! *hug*
login: You're back. First, drink this to warm up, then I'll help myself to your body... You're so warm I feel like I'm burning up. Ahahah!
main_extra: You feel like the temperature around me has gone up? Hahahah! I don't think you're just imagining it. I feel shy around you, which heats me up...|You wanna have a good time? Sure. We could sing, or go to the beach, or even... C-cook barbecue? Okay, that's enough teasing me... *blushes*|Heheh. Thanks for looking after me, Commander. It's refreshing. This feeling of codependence makes me think I won't be lonely again.
mission: Okay, I'll support you on this mission! When do we start?
touch: Getting to feel your warmth in this way... It's pretty nice.
touch2: If it helps you cool down, then I suppose... Wait, huh? Umm... *blushes*
win_mvp: Never forget – Mary is always by your side.

feeling5: Commander, are you sure it's fine for me to sit in your lap this whole time? Doesn't it get tiring...? But, being in your embrace really calms me down... There's no wind here, or rain, and it's really warm... I want it to last forever...
headtouch: Patting my head again? I'll have to pay you back for that. Crisps or cola? Take your pick.
login: Welcome back. I had the little guys clean the office... so you'll reward me with those crisps and cola as promised, right?
lose: Commander, if you spend more time with me... I might not be such a scaredy-cat then.
mail: Yeah, yeah, I'll go get the mail. What a pain... But since it's for your sake, I suppose I'll have to.
main_extra: I heard there's this place called "Potato Chip Rock." Think it's stuffed full of crisps? Commander, let's move it over to the port. ...Huh? There are no crisps there, nor is there any way of moving it?|Holding a conversation is such a pain... Wish I could make my coat big enough so I could hide myself entirely. Oh, but you'd be welcome to join me inside, heehee.|It's important to take breaks. Put all that work aside and go see if there's any cola in the fridge. Your fatigue's gonna melt away the moment you take a sip.
touch: ...Hm? You're all done with work, Commander? ...What a sneaky way of reminding me.
touch2: C-Commander, are you going on another treasure hunt...? Fine, fine. You should've just asked me first...

expedition: The commission team is back. They brought quite the haul!
feeling5: Now when I look at my dear treasure, I feel like it's worthless compared to you, Commander. That's not to say it's lost its value, just that you're so much more valuable than anything else... The question is, where can I hide you, my biggest treasure? Heehee♪
headtouch: Heehee. You can keep doing that, if you want.
home: Phew... You're back, safe and sound. I can finally relax... If you don't want me to worry, take me with you next time.
login: Welcome back. Here's your daily schedule. Take some people you can trust with you... and me.
main_extra: I'm heading out to inspect my treasure. Do you – the person I trust more than anyone else – want to come with me?|I get fidgety when you're not in my line of sight, for some reason... Oh, it's not that I'm worried you're doing something behind my back, I just start wondering if you're okay.|I've never stayed at a port for this long... This will probably be my home forever, and I will always be by your side.
touch: I will give you whatever you desire.
touch2: Such thirst... You should plunder me to satisfy it♪

detail: Give me your hand, Commander... There, I wrote a protective spell on it. Now clench. I only wrote it with my finger, but the effect should be the same. Heehee. Wherever you go now, the wind will watch over you.
feeling5: Have a gander at my newly-sorted display shelf! Everything on here is from our travels and memories together. I hope to expand my collection substantially and add many more shelves! Heehee.
headtouch: Hmph! You're getting it if you ruin my hair! Getting it, I say! ...Hahaha! I'm just joking!
home: Whydah told me about a thing called a "smartphone" which can create "photographs" of wondrous sights and things instantly. Could you bring one of those along the next time we leave the port?
login: Ah, I'm making some tea! Incidentally, are there any spices you dislike? I'll leave those out of the mixture.
main_extra: It's too quiet here... Shall I sing for you? What song would you like to hear?|You can't just sit down all day. Give me your hand and let's dance! Dancing is at its most fun when excitement is in the air!|Give me thy blessings and grant me everlasting protection... Heehee, I'm done praying. Now it's time to make you a very special dish!|Commander, look here! *snap*! I did it! Taking photographs with these smartphones is so convenient. It lets me collect sweet pictures of you whenever I want. Heehee. I'll treasure these dearly.

As the daughter of a noble family, I have much to learn from them.|So this is your office... It reminds me of my father's quarters.|Commander, excuse m—Oh, you're sound asleep? You might catch a cold like this though... Let me see if there's a blanket lying around.|Oh? I'm invited to attend today's tea party as well? Thank you very much. In return, I'll bring more of those sweets you said you enjoyed the last time.|I've seen many maids and butlers in my own world, but none as perfect as Miss Belfast. So devoted, yet also stern at times... She's certainly someone I want by my side.
mission: Let's finish our remaining missions quickly. I'll do everything I can to help you.
mission_complete: Well done. Once you've sorted out your rewards, would you like to have a tea break? I've even prepared sweets.
touch2: I assume you're ready to face the consequences?
win_mvp: That went well. Good work, everybody.

battle: The enemy's here. Stay sharp, everyone.
detail: How old am I? Does that really matter, Commander?
feeling5: What's wrong? Something on your mind? If there's something you want to get off your chest, just let it all out. It's not something I'd normally offer, but I'll make an exception today.
login: You're doing well, and that's what matters... Hm? Don't tell me you're half-asleep again. You really never change, do you?
main_extra: Go with you on a shopping trip? Ah, you must need a bodyguard. Rest assured, I've done it countless times before– Hm? Not quite?|Commander, stop sleeping on your desk and use your bed instead. You'll feel better rested that way.|Ever since you started training with me, you seem to be quicker on your feet. How about I test your abilities next time?|Ah, Bismarck... I was observing the Iron Blood exercise the other day, and her prowess impressed me. Commanding so many warriors while personally doing her utmost to lead her allies to victory... I doubt you'll find another warrior like her anywhere else.|The unsinkable Grand Old Lady who never misses a shot... While I don't know your full story, I can clearly tell you're a seasoned warrior. Now, why do you look so disgruntled? ...Hm? My build? What about it?
mission: Seems you still have work to do. I'm here if you need a hand.
mission_complete: All finished? Nicely done. I knew you could do it.
touch2: ...Sit down over there. I'm going to teach you some manners.
win_mvp: Your leadership is what let me fight so well. Thank you.

battle: They're coming. Everyone, stay alert.
detail: What is it, Commander? ...Never in my dreams would I have imagined inviting someone into my room. Anyway, please come on inside.
feeling5: That seed isn't what I'm looking for either. But since it's something you went through the trouble of looking for... I'll take good care of it.
login: Good morning... Where shall we go today?
main_extra: How old am I? Commander, you should know better than to ask a woman her age. But, I will say... we Orens have much longer lifespans than humans.|Looks like you're buried in work again, Commander. Is there anything I can help with? It's the least I can do.|In the midst of a journey chasing an impossible dream, spending some time like this might not be so bad after all...|I see that rabbit girl a lot whenever I'm out looking for seeds. She's almost always taking a nap though, just like right now... I wonder if I should wake her up.|I've heard you know a lot about the flowers of this world, Hanazuki. Do you know anything about a flower with great power? ...I see, thank you. By the way, that display over there is called... Ikebana? It's very beautiful.
mission: Seems like you still have some missions to get through... Let's make quick work of them, shall we?
mission_complete: Your rewards have arrived. I'd like you to check to see if there are any plants inside...
touch2: What an incorrigible human...
win_mvp: This was also made possible because of you...

battle: Folks, be careful not to get yourselves hurt!
detail: Hmm... I've found so many rare and fascinating curios in this world that my stash has become unmanageable. Commander, could you lend me a hand?
feeling5: The fruit you gave me the other day was marvelous! It's been a long time since my heart throbbed like that. You know me well, Commander! How could I expect any less?
login: Have you awoken, Commander? Why don't you take some time off and show me around the port? I'm sure that even you need time away from work.
main_extra: What's the matter? Would you like to chat with me? Heheh... No need to be shy. Come and sit next to me.|The genres of music in this world are prolific indeed. I happen to like this so-called "Classical" type. Listening to it is like rocking my heart to sleep...|Hehe, the ways of this world may be infecting me.|Friedrich der Große... Her lullaby is similar but different to the tones of our own world. But how beautiful and vigorous it is...|Yes, Ryuujou? Oh, is that a "dragon?" It's not exactly like the dragons I know... But I suppose one could say the same of this whole world, no?
mission: I find myself with no shortage of free time... You know what that means. Why don't I help out with some of your missions?
mission_complete: Finished your mission, have you? Then allow me to pamper you as reward.
touch2: *sigh*... Commander, will you ever learn to keep your hands to yourself? You are a tiresome one... Sit down and think about what you've done, you rascal.
win_mvp: Most spectacular leadership, Commander.

battle: Come, let us fight!
detail: I'm gonna treat you to my home cooking soon. You'll be able to taste the effort I put in!
feeling5: Meeting you was, I think, necessary for my growth as a shinobi. It without a doubt had a great impact that allowed me to take the next step as a person!
login: Oh! Commander! I waited for you! Come on, let's get going!
main_extra: What are your favorite things, Commander? Not just in terms of food, but also sports, music, and so on. I'm a little curious.|You say my training has paid off, but I won't feel satisfied until it pays off to an astonishing degree.|My grandpa, grandma, and classmates must all be worried about me... Even so, there are things in this world I have to do.|Shoukaku, hearing you play your flute reminds me of my home world – it strikes a chord with me!|What shinobi school are you from, Akatsuki? ...It's a secret? Thought as much. Secrecy is part of being a shinobi!
mission: You've got tasks left to do. Don't worry! I'll help you with them!
mission_complete: Wow, you finished your tasks! You never fail to impress!
touch2: I-I'm not a fan of when you touch me out of the blue...
win_mvp: I'd say my training has paid off, Commander.

battle: Behold my bladework!
detail: Commander, if you're tired, you should take some time to rest. Your efficiency will go up that way.
feeling5: When I was about to give up on everything, when I felt like I couldn't continue on any further, you were the one who took my hand, illuminated the way forward, and encouraged me to press on... Because I have someone like you, I am able to keep going... So please, continue watching over me just a bit longer.
login: Where have you been, Commander? We've all missed you.
main_extra: Now that I've finished up my shinobi training, I'd like to relax by working up a nice, easy sweat... Do you think you can provide me with your guidance?|I see quite a few people here practicing their sword techniques, but how do they maintain their blades? Are there any swordsmiths or sharpeners here?|Shopping around for some nice clothes can be quite refreshing... Commander, if you don't mind, do you think you could pick something out for us?|Miss Taihou's long black hair is always so lovely... How does she manage to take care of it?|Miss Akatsuki, are you also a shinobi just like us? Wow, to be both a ninja and a shipgirl... You must have had some superb training.
mission: It's almost time for work. I don't mind helping out, so please keep it up.
mission_complete: Looks like everything's taken care of. Thank you for your hard work. Would you like a shoulder massage?
touch2: W-wait, please! Don't stare at me like that...
win_mvp: Thank goodness... Everyone made it through safely.

battle: You're about to find out how I fight like!
detail: It's really struck me how hard it is to follow somebody's orders. That's not to say I hate it, though.
feeling5: Fighting used to be all I had... Or, it should've been. Now I'm at a bit of a loss, 'cause casually hanging out with you is more fun than I thought. Let me enjoy this period of uncertainty a little longer.
login: Hey, welcome back, Commander. You good? 'Cause I feel bad when you don't... Ah, never mind that! Let's get to work.
main_extra: Making bold moves is sweet. Taking the first step forward, then thinking afterwards... that's your specialty, isn't it?|While there's no such thing as training too much, I do take regular breaks so I don't make you worry.|Why do you touch me so much? Not saying I don't like it, just that it feels embarrassing past a point!|Yuudachi, I'll give you this meat if you help me with... Wait, what? Where'd the meat go? Hey! Did you just eat it whole?!|Akashi, I know you're busy, but could you have a look at my weapons? Huh? Payment? I'm not trying to sell them... What? Repair cost? Ugh, money-grubbing little...
mission: You've still got work to do. I'll help you out so we'll get it done quickly.
mission_complete: Finished a few tasks, huh? Man, you sure work hard. Then again, I like that about you.
touch2: Cut the boring crap. If you must, come at me head-on.
win_mvp: Heh! That's all they had? Too easy!

battle: Here I come!
detail: You wish to know everything about me? Surely you jest... All you need to know is that I exist to achieve justice.
feeling5: I can never repay you for the lengths you've gone for a hopeless woman with no knowledge of this world. Allow me to thank you once more, as I will again many more times to come.
login: Welcome back, Commander. Heehee. I'm pleased to be by your side, as always.
main_extra: Commander, will you help me choose an outfit in the days to come? Certainly, you may pick one according to your tastes. In fact, I'd prefer that.|This port is in no shortage of curiosities. My gaze constantly switches from one thing to the next.|I wonder how everyone back at Gessen is faring... That said, Minori is there to watch over them, so I may be worrying over nothing.|I feel that my skills have synergy with the ladies of the Northern Parliament. Especially with Gremyashchy – she's diligent, so I think my way of doing things would work well with her.|St. Louis, I've heard you teach people to dance. I'd like to learn the Western style of dancing – do you think you could instruct me, please?
mission: It appears you have unfinished business. Could I offer you some assistance, incapable though I may be?
mission_complete: You've finished your assignment? Most marvelous.
touch2: I am... not experienced with matters of impropriety.
win_mvp: It is an honor to fight alongside you all.

battle: I shall imprint the Never Returning's might upon your memory.
detail: You must care deeply about everyone who lives at this port. To tell the truth, it makes me slightly envious.
feeling5: You never fall prey to pessimism, and you lead us all with a positive attitude... How is one meant to stop idolizing a person such as you? Heehee... You shouldn't blush, or that blush will spread to me as well.
login: Welcome back, Commander. I've been waiting wearily for you... Heehee. That's not entirely false, you know.
main_extra: I'm sure Gekkō and Senkō would be very surprised if they saw how mellow I am now.|If Sirens are monsters that comprehend human language, they may have more in common with yōma than we think.|My second name, "Never Returning," would ward people off. Yet, the people of this world seem not to mind it very much.|Your apparel is quite similar to what we shinobi wear, Kuroshio. It appears to have all the same functions, too... Who made it, I wonder?
mission: You have a few tasks left to do. I shall help with them.
mission_complete: Oh? You've accomplished one of your tasks. Shall I turn it in for you?
touch2: Do you do this to other ladies as well?
win_mvp: It soothes my heart to see you're all okay.

battle: Okay. Let's do this.
detail: When I first saw people wearing riggings, walking around the port, I felt like I was surrounded by superheroes... Secretly, though, I was really scared.
feeling5: I think I can push myself just a little as long as I'm with you. So please, be kind to me until we've found a way to return to our home...
login: Welcome back. I'm glad to see you again... If you weren't here, I'd shut myself in my room.
main_extra: It's fun to hang out with people. And, as long as you're here, I don't feel scared...|Something smells friendly... *sniff sniff*... I think it's you, Commander.|I used to dislike going outside, but now I leave my room quite often... It's weird how things can change.|I-58, do you like quiet nights? Me too... I like it when it's quiet...|*sniff sniff*... You smell nice, Exeter... Like roses.|
mission: You still have unfinished missions. Maybe I could... help out, if you want?
mission_complete: You've finished a mission. With that done... could we have a short break?
touch2: You're right up next to me... But I don't mind...
win_mvp: Oh, we won... Can we go back now?

battle: Just leave it all to me! I'll deliver victory right into your hands!
detail: This place... is completely different from our village. But, after staying here for a while, it's starting to feel a bit like home... I'm getting used to it here.
feeling5: To be entirely honest, there's a problem that I haven't been able to discuss with you. But, it'll be okay. My friends and I will find a way to get by. I'm sure that it'll be alright... because of you, Commander.
login: W-welcome back. Commander, I was getting a bit lonely without you...
main_extra: As Tohno's leader, I have to do my best... but I still feel like I'm not strong enough...|I wonder how Tohno Village is doing these days... I'd really like to know, but the battle here is also very important right now.|This port has so much delicious food... I have to tell Ushi when I get back.|I always feel calm and at peace when Miss Illustrious is around.|Amagi-chan, you'll tell me all about the delicious food at this port, right?
mission: It looks like you can't keep up with your work... Shall I give you a hand...?
mission_complete: Since you're done with work... How about going for some tea once you've wrapped things up?
touch2: Commander... is this what gets you going? It's... rather embarrassing...
win_mvp: You had the guts to stand before ME... at least, your courage is worth acknowledging!
